OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779577462
OL,3,CUS and Iran closer to ending the war,
OL,4,Cofficials say
OL,6,FThe United States and Iran are closer
OL,7,Fto agreeing on a document of
OL,8,Funderstanding to end the war,
OL,9,Faccording to regional officials and a
OL,10,Fdiplomat.
OL,12,FIran suggested there were "narrowing
OL,13,Fdifferences" in the negotiations after
OL,14,FPakistan's army chief held further
OL,15,Fpeace talks in Tehran and US Secretary
OL,16,Fof State Marco Rubio told journalists
OL,17,Fin India that "there's been some
OL,18,Fprogress made" and "there may be news
OL,19,Flater today".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
