OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779577462
OL,3,CUS and Iran closer to ending the war,
OL,4,Cofficials say
OL,6,FThe officials expressed hope that a
OL,7,Ffinal decision on the Pakistan-
OL,8,Fprepared draft could come within 48
OL,9,Fhours as both sides review it. They
OL,10,Fspoke on condition of anonymity
OL,11,Fbecause they were not authorized to
OL,12,Ftalk to the media.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
