CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779577462
OL,3,CUS and Iran closer to ending the war,
OL,4,Cofficials say
OL,6,FThey said US Vice President JD Vance
OL,7,Fand envoys Steve Witkoff and Jared
OL,8,FKushner played significant roles in
OL,9,Fhelping bridge remaining gaps, and
OL,10,Fthat the Arab state of Qatar played a
OL,11,Fkey role by sending a senior official
OL,12,Fto Tehran, Iran, to support Pakistan's
OL,13,Fmediation efforts.
OL,15,FRubio repeated the US stance that Iran
OL,16,Fcan never have a nuclear weapon and
OL,17,Fmust turn over its highly enriched
OL,18,Furanium, and that the Strait of Hormuz
OL,19,Fmust be open.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
