FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779577462
OL,3,CUS and Iran closer to ending the war,
OL,4,Cofficials say
OL,6,FIranian state TV quoted foreign
OL,7,Fministry spokesperson Esmail Baghaei
OL,8,Fas describing the draft as a
OL,9,F"framework agreement", adding: "We
OL,10,Fwant this to include the main issues
OL,11,Frequired for ending the imposed war
OL,12,Fand other issues of essential
OL,13,Fimportance to us. Then, over a
OL,14,Freasonable time span, between 30 to 60
OL,15,Fdays, details are discussed and
OL,16,Fultimately a final agreement is
OL,17,Freached."
OL,19,FHe said the Strait of Hormuz is among
OL,20,Fthe topics discussed.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@UO]qD@`OUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
