PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779577462
OL,3,CUS and Iran closer to ending the war,
OL,4,Cofficials say
OL,6,FThe US and Israel sparked the war with
OL,7,Fattacks on February 28, cutting short
OL,8,Fnuclear talks with Iran. Tehran
OL,9,Fretaliated by effectively closing the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, a key waterway for
OL,11,Fthe region's oil, natural gas and
OL,12,Ffertiliser, causing global economic
OL,13,Fstrain.
OL,15,FThe US then blockaded Iranian ports.
OL,16,FThe US Central Command said on
OL,17,FSaturday that US forces had turned
OL,18,Faway more than 100 commercial vessels
OL,19,Fand disabled four since the blockade
OL,20,Fbegan on April 13.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
